---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'March 12, 2026';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy — Marty Beller">
	<section class="px-6 pb-8 pt-26.5">
		<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-max">
			<p class="font-accent text-base font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-white/60">Last updated {lastUpdated}</p>
			<h1 class="font-headline font-light leading-[0.83] tracking-tight text-6xl sm:text-7xl lg:text-8xl mt-3">
				PRIVACY POLICY.
			</h1>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="px-6 pb-20">
		<div class="mx-auto w-full max-w-max">
			<div class="flex flex-col gap-10 text-white/88">
				<p class="font-body text-xl leading-relaxed text-white/88">
					This Privacy Policy explains how Marty Beller collects, uses, and discloses information when you visit this website. This site is a basic informational website and uses Google Tag Manager to manage website tags and related measurement tools.
				</p>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Information We Collect</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						When you visit this website, certain information may be collected automatically, including your IP address, browser type, device information, approximate location, pages visited, time spent on pages, referring pages, and general interaction data.
					</p>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						If you contact us directly by email, we may receive any information you choose to provide in your message, such as your name, email address, and the contents of your communication.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">How We Use Information</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">We may use information we collect to:</p>
					<ul class="list-disc space-y-3 pl-6 font-body text-lg leading-relaxed marker:text-white/50">
						<li>operate and maintain the website;</li>
						<li>understand how visitors use the website;</li>
						<li>improve website content, performance, and user experience; and</li>
						<li>respond to inquiries or communications you send directly.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Google Tag Manager</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						This website uses Google Tag Manager, a tag management system provided by Google, to manage and deploy website tags. Google Tag Manager itself does not typically store personal information, but tags deployed through it may collect information about your use of the website, including through cookies or similar technologies.
					</p>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						Google may process information collected through tags managed by Google Tag Manager in accordance with its own policies. You can learn more by reviewing Google&rsquo;s privacy materials and any settings or controls Google makes available for its services.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Cookies</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						Cookies are small text files stored on your device. This website may use cookies or similar technologies in connection with tags managed through Google Tag Manager. Most browsers allow you to control cookies through their settings. Disabling cookies may affect how some parts of websites function.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Sharing of Information</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						We do not sell your personal information. We may share information with service providers that help operate the website, such as tag management, hosting, or analytics providers, or when required to comply with applicable law, regulation, legal process, or enforceable governmental request.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Data Retention</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						Information is retained for as long as reasonably necessary for the purposes described in this Privacy Policy or as otherwise required by law. Data retention related to tags or third-party tools may also be governed by the settings and policies of those providers.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Your Choices</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						You can limit or disable cookies through your browser settings. You may also review or manage privacy choices made available by Google or other third-party services used on the site. If you contact us and want us to delete correspondence you have sent directly, you may request that by email, subject to any legal or administrative retention needs.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Third-Party Links</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						This website may contain links to third-party websites. We are not responsible for the privacy practices, content, or policies of those third-party sites.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Children&rsquo;s Privacy</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						This website is not intended for children under 13, and we do not knowingly collect personal information from children under 13 through the website.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Changes to This Policy</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated effective date.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section class="flex flex-col gap-4">
					<h2 class="font-headline text-4xl font-normal leading-tight text-white">Questions</h2>
					<p class="font-body text-lg leading-relaxed">
						If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, you can contact Marty Beller at
						<a href="mailto:MartyBeller@gmail.com" class="font-semibold text-white underline decoration-white/30 underline-offset-4 transition hover:decoration-white">MartyBeller@gmail.com</a>.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>